* Visits, Visits Evolution, Unique Visits
* Actions, Action Evolution
* Pageviews, Pageviews Evolution
* Time on page
* Bounce rate
* Goal revenue
* Downloads
* and many more..

To define the condition you can select the conditions:

* Greater than, less than
* Equal, Not Equal
* Percentage increase/decrease

